1
00:01:07,040 --> 00:01:08,159
You've been

2
00:01:08,159 --> 00:01:09,519
cursed.

3
00:01:09,959 --> 00:01:11,159
Once it takes effect,

4
00:01:11,159 --> 00:01:11,920
it's very powerful.

5
00:01:11,920 --> 00:01:13,000
It not only harms the innocent,

6
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,079
but also affects you.

7
00:01:14,439 --> 00:01:15,879
You must be careful.

8
00:01:17,319 --> 00:01:19,480
[I must find a way to deal with it soon.]

9
00:01:22,480 --> 00:01:23,040
Your Highness,

10
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:25,200
I, Qing Lan,

11
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,239
pay my respects to you.

12
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,480
No formalities.

13
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,040
I'm no longer the Prince Xian.

14
00:01:32,799 --> 00:01:34,280
I only follow Your Highness.

15
00:01:34,879 --> 00:01:36,159
No matter who you are,

16
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,959
I will always be with you.

17
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,159
You suffered.

18
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:42,959
I was also victimized.

19
00:01:44,159 --> 00:01:45,159
But some things

20
00:01:45,159 --> 00:01:46,120
haven't been clarified yet,

21
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:47,599
so I had to take a risk.

22
00:01:47,599 --> 00:01:48,519
Don't worry, Your Highness.

23
00:01:48,680 --> 00:01:50,079
I will always be outside the door.

24
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,439
This can track people

25
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:28,199
to help you kill Meng Li.

26
00:02:30,719 --> 00:02:31,719
[Seeking Shadow Talisman.]

27
00:02:32,120 --> 00:02:33,800
[It can track the target]

28
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,000
[like a shadow.]

29
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,319
[But it's volatile,]

30
00:02:36,439 --> 00:02:37,599
[and will explode]

31
00:02:37,599 --> 00:02:38,479
[upon contact.]

32
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,759
[Once detonated,]

33
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:41,400
[it can turn a hundred miles into ashes,]

34
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,719
[leaving no life behind.]

35
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,919
[This talisman looks like a small plaque,]

36
00:02:44,919 --> 00:02:46,879
[but it must be implanted under the ear.]

37
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,520
[its effects start from the ear root,]

38
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,360
[spreading to the chest.]

39
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,560
[The curse is broken when the flesh and bones are broken,]

40
00:02:52,680 --> 00:02:54,000
[and the spirit manifests.]

41
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,479
[The resentment ends.]

42
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:06,000
[Mu Feishuang indeed has ulterior motives.]

43
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,400
[Li,]

44
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:18,199
[I, Shen Daozhi,]

45
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,719
[will never let you down in this life.]

46
00:03:21,159 --> 00:03:22,280
[If I ever let you down,]

47
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,599
[may I perish both body and soul.]

48
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,240
[The ties between people]

49
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,400
[come and go,]

50
00:03:31,680 --> 00:03:33,120
[but I never cared.]

51
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,639
[But your appearance]

52
00:03:36,280 --> 00:03:37,560
[gives me hope]

53
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,439
[and reluctance.]

54
00:03:42,840 --> 00:03:44,439
[The bond of lifetimes]

55
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,879
[should be the most precious.]

56
00:03:47,439 --> 00:03:49,039
[But I've let you down again and again.]

57
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,080
[I truly have no excuse,]

58
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,439
[and I can never repay.]

59
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:04,520
[Beside the water, in the clouds,]

60
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,039
[a myriad of spirits' nest.]

61
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,080
"Where the light is hidden."

62
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,599
Looks like we need to find a place

63
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:11,599
with water, a nest,

64
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,879
and a hidden light.

65
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:14,800
A'Li,

66
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:16,639
do you know where this is?

67
00:04:18,959 --> 00:04:20,480
A place with water and a nest

68
00:04:20,839 --> 00:04:21,800
is understandable,

69
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:24,439
but there are many places that fit.

70
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:26,600
We may not have time to search them all.

71
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,920
I can't figure out

72
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,560
what the hidden light means.

73
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,519
The place of dim light.

74
00:04:35,199 --> 00:04:35,959
The dim nest.

75
00:04:37,079 --> 00:04:38,240
Could it be Nether Mountain?

76
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:43,240
It was named Nether Mountain in recent years.

77
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:45,680
You Wencai wrote this poem a hundred years ago.

78
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,079
It couldn't be based on this mountain's name.

79
00:04:49,199 --> 00:04:50,000
Indeed.

80
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:53,480
So where exactly is the Water Cloud Rhinoceros hidden?

81
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,480
Sister Li,

82
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,240
someone wants to see you outside.

83
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,959
He's the one who killed Zhongjing.

84
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,759
How dare he show his face here?

85
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:06,920
Kill him!

86
00:05:07,079 --> 00:05:08,600
Avenge Zhongjing!

87
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:08,879
Yes!

88
00:05:08,879 --> 00:05:10,000
That's right!

89
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,720
Kill him!

90
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:13,000
Avenge Zhongjing!

91
00:05:13,319 --> 00:05:14,279
Kill him!

92
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:15,839
Kill him!

93
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,920
Stay calm!

94
00:05:24,240 --> 00:05:24,959
What are you here for?

95
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,800
I come to atone.

96
00:05:41,920 --> 00:05:42,639
I owe you,

97
00:05:43,079 --> 00:05:44,399
and to the whole Demon Clan.

98
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,000
Whatever you ask of me,

99
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:49,040
I, Shen Que, will gladly do it,

100
00:05:50,959 --> 00:05:53,120
hoping to make up for a fraction of the past.

101
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,800
You've repeatedly brought disaster upon the Demon Village.

102
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,040
Now you come with these grandiose words.

103
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:00,399
Don't think being a demon gives you a free pass.

104
00:06:03,720 --> 00:06:05,000
I took you along before

105
00:06:05,759 --> 00:06:07,759
because your demon power from devouring nightmares

106
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:08,639
could be of use to me.

107
00:06:09,879 --> 00:06:11,600
Now I have no time for your theatrics.

108
00:06:12,120 --> 00:06:12,920
You may leave.

109
00:06:27,439 --> 00:06:29,040
What trick are you up to now?

110
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:41,959
This...

111
00:06:42,399 --> 00:06:43,600
This is a tracking talisman

112
00:06:44,519 --> 00:06:46,319
Mu Feishuang placed on me.

113
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:47,879
It's called Shadow Seeker.

114
00:06:48,519 --> 00:06:50,800
In reality, it's meant to destroy the Demon Village.

115
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:54,439
The reason

116
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,279
we met at the Rhinoceros Moon Mountain

117
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,360
was because of it.

118
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,000
Now,

119
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,839
I'll take it out.

120
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,759
I just want you to trust me.

121
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,240
So what?

122
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,959
Once a demon dies, it dies for good.

123
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,680
Who knows what your true intentions are?

124
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,680
Get out of here!

125
00:07:18,360 --> 00:07:19,040
Go.

126
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,000
Go.

127
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:21,839
Go.

128
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:22,800
He's already a demon.

129
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,120
We can't just stand by and watch him die.

130
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,040
Prepare some herbs for him.

131
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,240
As for the rest,

132
00:07:28,879 --> 00:07:30,120
it's up to his own fate.

133
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,879
They...

134
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:59,120
They cured me.

135
00:08:00,199 --> 00:08:01,399
Seems

136
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:03,199
pixies are kinder

137
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:05,240
than humans.

138
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,879
Come catch me!

139
00:08:21,720 --> 00:08:22,839
Slow down!

140
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:25,480
Wait for me!

141
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:36,840
Which way?

142
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:37,559
Huh?

143
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,159
Come get me!

144
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:49,919
Hurry up!

145
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,679
I'm sorry.

146
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:24,960
Little Bell Spirit,

147
00:09:26,399 --> 00:09:27,720
you died because of me.

148
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,639
I know

149
00:09:29,639 --> 00:09:30,840
no matter what I say

150
00:09:31,519 --> 00:09:32,120
or do now,

151
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:33,919
it's all useless.

152
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:36,080
No matter how many apologies I make,

153
00:09:37,519 --> 00:09:39,200
I can't bring you back.

154
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:44,600
Now that I've seen

155
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:46,039
and understood everything,

156
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:48,559
I'll face the consequences.

157
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:50,519
I deserve

158
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:53,600
this pain.

159
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,240
You think

160
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:01,879
a few

161
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:02,919
sugary words

162
00:10:03,639 --> 00:10:04,679
can fix this?

163
00:10:05,799 --> 00:10:06,799
Some mistakes

164
00:10:07,360 --> 00:10:08,559
are irreversible.

165
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,720
I'm sorry.

166
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:29,919
I know everything.

167
00:10:29,919 --> 00:10:31,080
Our past.

168
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:34,559
The one you loved killed your friend.

169
00:10:35,200 --> 00:10:36,759
It must have hurt you deeply.

170
00:10:39,679 --> 00:10:41,919
The one I shared a past with is long dead.

171
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,399
You killed the innocent Zhong Jing.

172
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,559
This hatred,

173
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:50,720
I will never forget.

174
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:55,039
I know you hate me.

175
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:56,879
Although everyone saw

176
00:10:57,240 --> 00:10:59,399
I killed Zhong Jing that day,

177
00:10:59,399 --> 00:11:02,120
the final blow wasn't my intention.

178
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:04,039
I was in a trance,

179
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:06,320
and didn't realize what I was doing.

180
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:08,000
Even now,

181
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,279
you're still lying!

182
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:14,679
I, Shen Que, swear on my life,

183
00:11:15,559 --> 00:11:16,799
everything I'm about to say

184
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,440
is the truth.

185
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,519
The day Zhong Jing was killed,

186
00:11:20,879 --> 00:11:22,559
I did cast a Immobilize Spell on her,

187
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,000
to calm her spirit,

188
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:25,039
and still the waters,

189
00:11:25,799 --> 00:11:28,000
hoping to find a way to break the barrier.

190
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,240
But I never intended to kill her.

191
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,200
By the time I came to my senses,

192
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:55,799
she was already...

193
00:11:56,039 --> 00:11:57,120
You mean

194
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:58,600
you were controlled?

195
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,559
You think a few words will fool me?

196
00:12:18,279 --> 00:12:19,440
What did you just do?

197
00:12:19,759 --> 00:12:21,200
This is Qingdu Temple's secret technique.

198
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,440
It can make the person

199
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,399
lose consciousness temporarily

200
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:26,759
and be controlled by the caster.

201
00:12:27,159 --> 00:12:28,200
Your actions just now

202
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,159
were controlled by me.

203
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:34,679
I just want you to be on guard.

204
00:12:35,279 --> 00:12:36,320
Don't let the tragedy

205
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:37,879
from happening again.

206
00:12:51,639 --> 00:12:53,360
You're still so kind,

207
00:12:54,480 --> 00:12:55,879
even as a bell.

208
00:12:57,000 --> 00:12:58,279
Still so soft-hearted.

209
00:12:59,039 --> 00:13:00,720
The Spirit died because of me.

210
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,440
No matter what I say,

211
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,960
I can't make up for even a fraction of it.

212
00:13:05,720 --> 00:13:07,639
Let her rest in peace

213
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:09,039
by this murmuring stream,

214
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,480
in this deep, dark cave.

215
00:13:12,879 --> 00:13:13,799
What did you say?

216
00:13:16,159 --> 00:13:16,919
I said,

217
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:18,840
I can't make up for even a fraction of it.

218
00:13:18,840 --> 00:13:19,559
Not that one.

219
00:13:21,639 --> 00:13:23,759
May she rest in peace

220
00:13:23,879 --> 00:13:25,039
in this tranquil place.

221
00:13:26,480 --> 00:13:29,200
Actually, this is already good enough.

222
00:13:29,799 --> 00:13:31,159
The Demon Clan,

223
00:13:31,159 --> 00:13:32,159
with its gurgling waters

224
00:13:32,639 --> 00:13:34,519
and radiant glow,

225
00:13:34,639 --> 00:13:36,120
is fortunate to guard such a beautiful place.

226
00:13:36,360 --> 00:13:39,320
Clouds and waters

227
00:13:39,679 --> 00:13:42,399
dance in harmony.

228
00:13:42,919 --> 00:13:45,799
Millions of spirits

229
00:13:45,960 --> 00:13:49,159
[In the depths of the abyss, the holy rhino is found.]

230
00:13:49,960 --> 00:13:51,720
[Shattered dreams, lingering affection.]

231
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:53,000
[Heaven and earth overturned.]

232
00:13:53,279 --> 00:13:56,639
[Profound amber sinks into the abyss, the calamity ends.]

233
00:13:57,639 --> 00:13:59,120
[The murmuring waters.]

234
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:00,759
[Clouds and waters.]

235
00:14:01,919 --> 00:14:03,080
[It's the Xianyin Pool.]

236
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,559
[Millions of demons' nest.]

237
00:14:05,120 --> 00:14:06,279
[It's the Demon Village.]

238
00:14:06,840 --> 00:14:08,039
[The radiant glow.]

239
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,919
[The radiant glow is...]

240
00:15:01,480 --> 00:15:03,159
[What I've been seeking for so long.]

241
00:15:03,919 --> 00:15:05,279
[is far away from the sky,]

242
00:15:05,600 --> 00:15:06,720
[but close at hand.]
